</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_208" id="103v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Hern Jorgen von Seckendorff czu Gneczheim </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber her Jörg, uns hat fürgelegt <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Rumel,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, wie daz man dem
                            <expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Goltfusz czu Kreyendorff,
                                <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>armman<ex>n</ex></expan>, funff pferde bey der naht ausz
                                <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan> hause genomen hab, die czu ew gen
                        Gneczheim <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> sein.
                            <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir dem
                                <expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> burgers armman <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
                        hilff und <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> beweisen und auch mit den, die
                        das getan <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, schicken wöllet, daz dem
                                <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>armman<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> seine pferde
                            <expan>widerwerde<ex>n</ex></expan>. Als etc. Das
                            <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
